text: Ðæs cempa hine gehet David ofslaa fore hire ðingum Bersabe wæs hire noma ðy wæs Salomones moder ðæs cyniges.
Uutodlice suæ wæs cristes cneureso.
To gemanne nalles to habbanne for wif.
Abiathar ðe aldormon wæs in ðæm tid in Hierusalem forebiscob; He bebeod Maria Iosephe to gemenne and to begeonganne mið claennisse.
In Esaia.
In ðær byrig capharnaum is genemned and Maritimam cuoeð forðon ðyu burg is on sae; ðyus burug hæfis suiðe micel traht and miclo geryno.
Eadge biðon ða ðaerfendo, þæt is unspoedge menn<../images/lbar.gif>unsynnige forðon hia agan <godes>.
Forðon ða milde <gebyes> <hlifgiendra> eorðo.
Eadge biðon ða ðe ðyrstas and hyncgras æfter soðfæstnisse forðon ða gefylled biðon in ece lif.
Eadge biðon ða clæne hearte bute esuice and eghwoelcum facne forðon hia geseas God in ecnisse.
Eadge biðon ða friðgeorne ða ðe hea buta eghwoelcum flita and toge <behaldas> ða sint Godes <suna> genemned.
<../images/lbar.gif>sint ða ane<../images/lbar.gif>aron ða ane.
Mamon, þæt is gidsunges hlaferd ðe diowl; He is sua genemned Mammonis.
Gegerues God suiðor alle ðingo hæfeð us gesald monnum bi allum wihtum.
Cueð halig þæt is ðy halga gesaegdnisse æt hundum nere gesald þæt is unwyrðum and unclænum monnum.

Þæt Aron þa meregrotta þæt sindon godspelles bebodo;Ante porcosbefore bergum ðæt sindon ða mæstelbergas þæt Aron ða gehadade menn and ða gode menn and ða wlonce men forhogas Godes bebod and godspelles.
Ðæm ðe tuas ymb Godes mæht him forstondes mæht and geleafa fore is ungelefnise.

Cueð to ðæm apostolum & biscopum æfter him forðmest unboht gehad fengon & unboht<../images/lbar.gif>unceap buta eghuelcum worðe seallas ðæm ðe sie wyrðe<../images/lbar.gif>worð bið in lare & in ð<../images/etail.gif>wum & in clænnise & in cystum & in lichoma hælo forðon biscop scæl cunnege & leornege ðone preost <georne> buta ær geleornade.
Biscope is forboden þæt he onfoe <niwecumenum> <preostum> & to gehælgenne ferunga.
<Leorn> hine ærest & ge gecunnia & arca <ge> ða ðe hine cunn huulic monn se is lar <gesceauig> buta he <hæbb> unforcuð <uitnesse>.
Biscope is <forboden> þæt he onfoe <niwe> cunenum <preost> & to gehælgenne ferunga.
<Leorne> hine ærest & <georne> gecunnia & <ascage> ða ðe hine <cunnas> huulic monn se <sie>.
<Ne> <his> lar <gesceauige> buta he <hæbbe> unforcuð <vitnesse>.
Þæt wæs ðæra Iudea sunnadæg.
Iðæs cyninges broðer laf þæt wæs hire dohter.
<../images/lbar.gif>eis.him.
Ða apostolas woendon þætte he woere yfel wiht and walde hea besuica.
Iðer monn <tred> ða winbegera.
<centurio><hundfre>.
Ðas Aron wyrto noma biðon in lehtunum.
<../images/lbar.gif>sua long gie ne dedon anum ðassa metdmaasta.
In temple.
